            <td valign="top" width="50%" align="left"></td>
         </tr>
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td colspan="2"><strong>Subfield Codes</strong><br></td>
         </tr>
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td colspan="1">$a - Exhibitions note (NR) <br>$3 - Materials specified (NR) <br>$5 - Institution to which field applies (NR) <br></td>
            <td colspan="1">$6 - Linkage (NR) <br>$8 - Field link and sequence number (R) <br></td>
         </tr>
   </table>
      <hr>
      <h3>FIELD DEFINITION AND SCOPE</h3>
      <p>Copy-specific field that contains a note which cites exhibitions where the material
                  described has been shown.      </p>
      <hr>
      <h3>GUIDELINES FOR APPLYING CONTENT DESIGNATORS</h3>
      <h4><span class="box">&#9632;</span> INDICATORS
      </h4>
      <ul>
         <li>Both indicators are undefined; each contains a blank (#).</li>
      </ul>
      <h4><span class="box">&#9632;</span> SUBFIELD CODES
      </h4>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$a - Exhibitions note</strong> <div class="description">Entire text of the note.</div>
         <div class="example">
            <table width="100%">
               <tr>
                  <td valign="top" width="5%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="15%" align="left"></td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left"><strong>585</strong></td>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>##</strong><strong>$a</strong>Exhibited: "Visions of City &amp; Country: Prints
                                             and Photographs of Nineteenth-Century France," organized by Worchester Art
                                             Museum and the American Federation of Arts, 1982.
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$3 - Materials specified</strong> <div class="description">Part of the described materials to which the field applies.</div>
         <div class="example">
            <table width="100%">
               <tr>
                  <td valign="top" width="5%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="15%" align="left"></td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left"><strong>585</strong></td>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>##</strong><strong>$3</strong>Color lithographs<strong>$a</strong>Exhibited: "Le Brun &agrave; Versailles," sponsored by the
                                             Cabinet des dessins, Mus&eacute;e du Louvre, 1985-1986.
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$5 - Institution to which field applies</strong> <div class="description">See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control
                                       Subfields</a></em>.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$6 - Linkage</strong> <div class="description">See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control
                                       Subfields</a></em>.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$8 - Field link and sequence number</strong> 
        <div class="description">See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control
                                       Subfields</a></em>.
        </div>
   </div>
      <hr>
      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Punctuation</strong> - Field 585 ends with a period unless another mark of punctuation is present. If the final
                     subfield is subfield $5, the mark of punctuation precedes that subfield.
      </div>
